title: Will Smith: Fresh Prince to Fallen King | A Low Down Dirty Shame | 3
description:
Jada Pinkett came from an unstable home life that taught her she could only rely on herself. But her talent for acting takes her to Hollywood, where she pursues her dream of being onscreen. But then Will Smith happens. And even though she’s madly in love with their beautiful family, she worries she’s being consumed by his wants and needs and losing her own identity. Until one day… when she makes her voice heard.
